        "subject": "LU-591 MRP-139 set LDISKFS_FEATURE_INCOMPAT_DIRDATA on upgrade",
        "message": "LU-591 MRP-139 set LDISKFS_FEATURE_INCOMPAT_DIRDATA on upgrade\n\n1.8 code supports the feature not since 1.8.0, so it was disabled\nby default in upgrade cases. however, as we maintain the upgrade/downgrade\non 1 version only, it is already safe to enable it by default.\n\nChange-Id: I36b0246c38b24f5f4970b9f6cd93d266206f541e\nReviewed-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Nathan Rutman <Nathan_Rutman@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\n"
